  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the fernbrake and gosari and stir to combine.",
    "Add the diced tomato and cook until the mixture is heated through.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Use a spatula to create a well in the center of the skillet and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve the charred molten Kenyan fernbrake gosari skillet hot."
